# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES REFERENCE
# Copy this file to .env.local in the respective package directory
# and fill in your actual values
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# packages/hardhat/.env.local
# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# DEPLOYER_PRIVATE_KEY=0x...
# ETHERSCAN_V2_API_KEY=...
# ALCHEMY_API_KEY=...
# SUBSCRIPTION_ID=...
# TREASURY_ADDRESS=0x...
# REPORT_GAS=false

# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# packages/nextjs/.env.local
# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# NEXT_PUBLIC_ALCHEMY_API_KEY=...
# NEXT_PUBLIC_WALLET_CONNECT_PROJECT_ID=...
# NEXT_PUBLIC_LOTTERY_CONTRACT_ADDRESS=0x...
# NEXT_PUBLIC_TREASURY_ADDRESS=0x...
# NODE_ENV=development

# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# KEY GENERATION INSTRUCTIONS
# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# 1. Generate a new deployer account (REQUIRED - old key is compromised):
#    cd packages/hardhat
#    yarn account:generate
#    Then export the private key to DEPLOYER_PRIVATE_KEY

# 2. Get API Keys:
#    - Alchemy: https://dashboard.alchemyapi.io
#    - Etherscan: https://etherscan.io/apis
#    - Reown (WalletConnect): https://cloud.reown.com
#    - Coinmarketcap (optional): https://coinmarketcap.com/api

# 3. Set up Chainlink VRF (Sepolia):
#    - Go to: https://vrf.chain.link/sepolia
#    - Create a subscription and get SUBSCRIPTION_ID
#    - VRF_COORDINATOR and KEY_HASH should already be set (Sepolia testnet)

# 4. Set Treasury Address:
#    - This is where lottery fees will be sent
#    - Should be a secure multi-sig wallet in production
